  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase III Study, double-blind, comparing association of anti-inflammatory and anti-rheumatic
      in 375 subjects with knee osteoarthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation after 12 weeks of treatment, in 3 arms, the efficacy and safety of the
      association.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
